WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Surely among you there is someone interested in music,

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
sound, acoustics...

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Well, my beginnings were somewhat similar;

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.000
since I was a kid, I was very interested in music

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.000
and started exploring the sound of different instruments

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.000
such as the guitar.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
But over time that interest began to grow

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.000
and I became more interested in knowing what was hidden behind the sound,

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
knowing how to control it.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:31.000
It was that desire to know that led me to study <i>Sound Engineering</i>.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.000
