00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Throughout my career and academic training

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.000
I had the opportunity to learn about the various branches of acoustics.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.000
For example: <i>architectural acoustics</i>,

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.000
or acoustics applied in the <i>environmental</i> or <i>industrial</i> fields.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Each project I worked on

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:55.000
gave me the opportunity to combine my passion for design

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:58.000
with the technical knowledge I acquired

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:02.000
to design spaces that were not only aesthetically pleasing,

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:05.000
but spaces that improved quality of life

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.000
through sound.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:10.000
