00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:15.000
each of the projects I tackled allowed me to expand my knowledge

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:19.000
and understand how sound affects our daily lives.

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:23.000
Therefore, my goal as a Sound Engineer is to use that knowledge

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:26.000
to improve quality of life

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.000
and the quality of our environment

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.000
by proposing innovative solutions.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:37.000
If any of you are interested in learning how <i>Sound Engineering</i> can make a difference,

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:43.000
I invite you to explore my web portfolio where you will find the works and projects I have worked on;

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.000
